oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carl Smith and Bobby Wright and Girl Vocalist
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing; Smith, Carl, 1927-2010; Wright, Bobby;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising Carl Smith and the Tunesmiths, Bobby Wright, and a girl vocalist. The negative that would have contained information on the talent agency is missing. The negatives would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
